Here are the authoritative public test cases for feature4_toolbar_position:
{
  "description": "Computes where a floating formatting toolbar should be placed so it is horizontally centered over the current text selection and sits a fixed gap above it. Inputs are the selection rectangle, the editor's bounding rectangle, and the toolbar size; outputs are the toolbar's top and left offsets relative to the editor.",
  "cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "command": "toolbar_position",
        "range_rect": {
          "top": 0,
          "left": 0,
          "right": 1
        },
        "editor_rect": {
          "top": 0,
          "left": 0
        },
        "toolbar": {
          "width": 0,
          "height": 0
        }
      },
      "expected_output": "offset_top=-14\noffset_left=0.5\n"
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "command": "toolbar_position",
        "range_rect": {
          "top": 100,
          "left": 40,
          "right": 140
        },
        "editor_rect": {
          "top": 20,
          "left": 10
        },
        "toolbar": {
          "width": 60,
          "height": 36
        }
      },
      "expected_output": "offset_top=30\noffset_left=50\n"
    }
  ]
}

Here are the authoritative public test cases for feature3_2_remove_link:
{
  "description": "Removing a hyperlink from a previously linked, non-empty selection detaches the link entity from the text. The output reports the URL that existed before removal and that no entity remains attached afterward.",
  "cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "command": "remove_link",
        "text": "Hello World!",
        "anchor_offset": 0,
        "focus_offset": 5,
        "link": "http://www.globo.com"
      },
      "expected_output": "url_before=http://www.globo.com\nentity_after=none\n"
    }
  ]
}

Here are the authoritative public test cases for feature3_1_apply_link:
{
  "description": "Applying a hyperlink to a selected text range stores a link entity carrying the target URL. When the entered address has no scheme, a default http:// scheme is prepended; an address that already starts with http:// or https:// is stored unchanged.",
  "cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "command": "add_link",
        "text": "Hello World!",
